Abstract Factory - Factory of factories.
Factory that creates other factories related by families or grouping.

When to use?
When we have family of products (multiple factories).

For example,
Interface - Shape: SQUARE, CIRCLE (ShapeFactory)
Interface - Color: RED, BLACK (ColorFactory)



Decorating room example:

We need 2 tables: one from wood, second from steel
- For wooden - we need carpenter shop
- For steel - we need ready-made steel shop
both of these are table factories

we decide what kind of factory we need
